Resistance.help: Diabolique's Spirits are non corporeal and highly resistant to Immobilization, smashing, lethal and negative energy damage. However, they are vulnerable to Energy and Psionic damage.

Ethereal.help: Diabolique's Spirits can make themselves Ethereal and shift out of the material plane. Ethereal Spectres are invisible, and cannot affect or be affected by those in normal space.
